</p>

<h2 id = "rona">Rona - člověk sico</h2>
<p>
<ul>
  <li style = "float: left; width: 400px;"><div style = "width: 90px; float: left;">síla:</div> <strong style = "float: left;">13/+1</strong></li>
  <li style = "float: left; width: 400px;"><div style = "width: 90px; float: left;">obratnost:</div> <strong style = "float: left;">17/+3</strong></li>
  <li style = "float: left; width: 400px;"><div style = "width: 90px; float: left;">odolnost:</div> <strong style = "float: left;">11/0</strong></li>
  <li style = "float: left; width: 400px;"><div style = "width: 90px; float: left;">inteligence:</div> <strong style = "float: left;">13/+1</strong></li>
  <li style = "float: left; width: 400px;"><div style = "width: 90px; float: left;">charisma:</div> <strong style = "float: left;">17/+3</strong></li>
  <li style = "float: left; width: 400px;"><div style = "width: 90px; float: left;">životy:</div> <strong style = "float: left;">26</strong></li>
